<a class="authorName" itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/197865.Richard_Lloyd_Parry"><span itemprop="name">Richard Lloyd Parry</span></a> <span class="greyText">(Goodreads Author)</span>
</div>
</span>

