<span id="freeTextContainer14348623038824664596">Fascinating true crime story of Lucie Blackman&apos;s disappearance in Japan. From Parry&apos;s reporting readers learn about not only Lucie and her attacker, but also much about Japan itself.</span>
  <span id="freeText14348623038824664596" style="display:none">Fascinating true crime story of Lucie Blackman's disappearance in Japan. From Parry's reporting readers learn about not only Lucie and her attacker, but also much about Japan itself.</span>
